answers.body_markdown:
Hi in your RestController you have this code:

    private CompanyManager mgr;
    
        public void setUserManager(CompanyManager companyManager) {
            this.mgr = companyManager;
        }

BUT CompanyManager mgr are not decalred in this way!

you must set `@Autowired`

    private CompanyManager mgr;

        @Autowired
        public void setUserManager(CompanyManager companyManager) {
            this.mgr = companyManager;
        }


And your CompanyManager must be Tagged with @Service

**Be carefull, if it is possible you can also solve this problem with JPA / JPQL.** it will be much easer for you - you dont need to write to much code.

