answers.body_markdown:
The reason for this is that spring boot is using `querydsl-bom` which has defined the wrong library artifact id. It has defined the id as 

     &lt;dependency&gt;
          &lt;groupId&gt;com.querydsl&lt;/groupId&gt;
          &lt;artifactId&gt;querydsl-codegen-utils&lt;/artifactId&gt;
          &lt;version&gt;5.0.0&lt;/version&gt;
     &lt;/dependency&gt;

whereas the exact library that has to be present is 

     &lt;dependency&gt;
          &lt;groupId&gt;com.querydsl&lt;/groupId&gt;
          &lt;artifactId&gt;codegen-utils&lt;/artifactId&gt;
          &lt;version&gt;5.0.0&lt;/version&gt;
     &lt;/dependency&gt;

Reference:- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/com.querydsl/querydsl-bom/5.0.0

Issue is fixed in querydsl-bom but never released a new version for it https://github.com/querydsl/querydsl/commit/c589757291d4f53e6148dae3227bed111c2f740f

